&lt;h3 id="解压latex镜像">解压latex镜像&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e8%a7%a3%e5%8e%8blatex%e9%95%9c%e5%83%8f" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
