&lt;h3 id="检查latex安装是否正常">检查Latex安装是否正常。&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e6%a3%80%e6%9f%a5latex%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85%e6%98%af%e5%90%a6%e6%ad%a3%e5%b8%b8" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
